{"tid":847252,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【魔法棒扑婆婆】雙眼紅腫如雞蛋 白蘭花婆婆：告到佢終身監禁","createTime":"2018-10-04T04:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T05:09:10.000Z","uid":78070,"like":111,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d4bcec0399be45813d9a8c772721f145f67fdfcb","tid":847252,"uid":78070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"在深水埗擺地攤賣白蘭花的葉婆婆，前日下午遭一名金髮女子用掃帚襲擊，頭破血流。連日來葉婆婆都沒有擺檔，今日《蘋果》記者終於找到她，只見她雙眼紅腫如雞蛋，看住令人心酸。她憤然道：「告佢，一定告佢終身監禁。」<br />\n<br />\n葉婆婆連續兩天沒有外出擺檔，記者到她位於黃大仙的住所探望。葉婆婆開門，只見她兩隻眼睛紅腫如雞蛋，前額貼上膠布，一頭白髮也要用髮夾夾起來，以免觸及傷口。猶幸婆婆精神不錯，聲若洪鐘。她表示事件令她暫時無法開檔「影響工作？梗係有啦！人哋食政府糧，食到屙都屙唔晒，我就乜都冇。」意思指自己自力更生，但如今手停口停。<br />\n<br />\n對於事件的經過，她不願詳談，只謂不認識該名女子，並着記者去控告對方。「你去差館告佢，一定告佢終身監禁。」然後匆匆關上大門。<br />\n<br />\n事發於前日(周二)下午3時，69歲的葉婆婆在汝州街與桂林街交界的路口擺地攤，賣白蘭花及藥油，隨行更有一架手推車，放有大袋花生等食物。其間被一名金髮女子指她阻街，雙方因而起爭執。女子拿起魔法杖拍打婆婆，致頭破血流。警方到場拘捕姓木之本(40歲)女子涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/04/123824_1c876361dd9c41e8cf5cbaa679fa5eed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F04%2F123824_1c876361dd9c41e8cf5cbaa679fa5eed.jpg&h=983fb743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181004/58754359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58754359&d=HOg1Gf%2FEMHIvan3hf%2B7tMjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=59c3e9ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58754359&h=6805a2b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181004/58754359</a><br />\n<br />\n動物台台主木之本櫻為咗消滅阻街廢老回收古羅卡，竟然落得如此下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99de55137c8b43f8fce75d9c32e6cca34b277ed7","tid":847252,"uid":7840,"like":86,"dislike":6,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:12:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"528198ddf3128f15d4dcc389c327b0665c757bef","tid":847252,"uid":7638,"like":2,"dislike":64,"score":-62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"coser黎？定痴線婆黎？掃把報紙寫魔法杖又係做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0838e6f1c0e5ff6355b24b554c0621934fc20a8","tid":847252,"uid":61300,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"估錯左內容，我出返去先"},{"pid":"26d2a60022c997f7508b11a67c7f7b751bc0704c","tid":847252,"uid":100347,"like":51,"dislike":10,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:31:29.000Z","msg":"檢控係刑事<br />\n告係民事<br />\n<br />\n阿婆睇得多膠劇唔識分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb144bed72cca4ec4aeed25df482e38fca84697","tid":847252,"uid":2772,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:32:36.000Z","msg":"呀婆要死先有機會告到終身喎"},{"pid":"1bc0bf40dd4b46b1da33148987bf720e3bbcc2fc","tid":847252,"uid":54880,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"528198ddf3128f15d4dcc389c327b0665c757bef","tid":847252,"uid":7638,"like":2,"dislike":64,"score":-62,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"coser黎？定痴線婆黎？掃把報紙寫魔法杖又係做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:33:41.000Z","msg":"真心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"91eb960e19e716395c73ff19f739b3953c600961","tid":847252,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"咪撚抄po啦"},{"pid":"20c4aae21941749d20bec2e87d134b20ce750c82","tid":847252,"uid":35667,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T05:34:55.000Z","msg":"coser冇個正常仲要40歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acff18cf1f16dde1dfd3b49bf53b2865960e4204","tid":847252,"uid":152598,"like